TREASURY AUTHORIZED

THROUGH DECEMBER 31, 2020 THAT PROVIDES FOR A SYSTEM OF SHARED PUBLIC AND PRIVATE COMPENSATION FOR CERTAIN INSURED LOSSES RESULTING FROM CERTIFIED ACTS OF TERRORISM. FOR A FURTHER DESCRIPTION

