MAINTAINING CAPITAL LEVELS COMMENSURATE WITH THE COMPANY'S DESIRED RATINGS FROM INDEPENDENT RATING AGENCIES, FUNDING OF THE COMPANY'S QUALIFIED PENSION PLAN, CAPITAL REQUIREMENTS OF THE COMPANY'S

