$14 MILLION OF NET REALIZED INVESTMENT GAINS RELATED TO EQUITY SECURITIES, $7 MILLION OF NET REALIZED INVESTMENT GAINS FROM REAL ESTATE SALES AND $17 MILLION OF NET REALIZED

