AND NET WRITTEN PREMIUMS IN EACH SEGMENT IN 2016 AND 2015 AS COMPARED WITH THE RESPECTIVE PRIOR YEAR ARE DISCUSSED IN MORE DETAIL IN THE SEGMENT DISCUSSIONS THAT FOLLOW.

