121

TABLE OF CONTENTS

(2)

REPRESENTS

AGREEMENTS ENTERED INTO IN THE ORDINARY COURSE OF BUSINESS TO LEASE OFFICE SPACE, EQUIPMENT AND FURNITURE. FUTURE SUBLEASE RENTAL INCOME AGGREGATING

APPROXIMATELY $4 MILLION WILL PARTIALLY OFFSET THESE COMMITMENTS.

