TRUST DEPOSIT AT DECEMBER 31, 2016 AND 2015, WHEREBY OWNED SECURITIES WITH A FAIR VALUE OF APPROXIMATELY $97 MILLION AND $140 MILLION, RESPECTIVELY, HELD BY AN INSURANCE

SUBSIDIARY WERE PLEDGED INTO A LLOYD'S TRUST ACCOUNT TO SUPPORT CAPITAL REQUIREMENTS FOR THE COMPANY'S OPERATIONS AT LLOYD'S.

