EXPERIENCE IN THE HOMEOWNERS AND OTHER PRODUCT LINE FOR (I) NON-CATASTROPHE WEATHER-RELATED LOSSES FOR ACCIDENT YEAR 2013 AND (II) CATASTROPHE LOSSES FOR ACCIDENT YEARS 2011 THROUGH

2013.

