(ASSUMING A 360-DAY YEAR CONSISTING OF TWELVE 30- DAY MONTHS) AT THE THEN CURRENT TREASURY RATE (AS DEFINED IN THE SENIOR NOTES), PLUS 20 BASIS POINTS. ON OR AFTER NOVEMBER 15, 2045, THE SENIOR

NOTES MAY BE REDEEMED, IN WHOLE OR IN PART, AT THE COMPANY'S OPTION, AT ANY TIME OR FROM TIME TO TIME, AT A

