(1)

THE

FAIR VALUE ESTIMATES OF THE TWO PRIVATE EQUITY FUNDS COMPRISING THESE INVESTMENTS ARE DETERMINED BY AN EXTERNAL FUND MANAGER BASED ON RECENT FILINGS, OPERATING

RESULTS, BALANCE SHEET STABILITY, GROWTH AND OTHER BUSINESS AND MARKET SECTOR FUNDAMENTALS. DUE TO THE SIGNIFICANT UNOBSERVABLE INPUTS IN THESE VALUATIONS, THE TOTAL FAIR VALUE ESTIMATES ARE DISCLOSED

IN LEVEL 3.

THE

BALANCE OF LEVEL 3 FAIR VALUE INVESTMENTS WAS $2 MILLION AT DECEMBER 31, 2015 AND THE CHANGE IN BALANCE FROM THE PRIOR YEAR WAS INSIGNIFICANT.

