TABLE OF CONTENTS

CODE OF ETHICS

THE COMPANY HAS ADOPTED A CODE OF BUSINESS CONDUCT AND ETHICS (CODE OF ETHICS) THAT APPLIES TO ALL EMPLOYEES, INCLUDING EXECUTIVE OFFICERS, AND

TO DIRECTORS. THE CODE OF ETHICS IS AVAILABLE ON THE CORPORATE GOVERNANCE PAGE OF THE COMPANY'S INTERNET WEBSITE AT

WWW.TRAVELERS.COM

. IF THE COMPANY

EVER WERE TO AMEND OR WAIVE ANY PROVISION OF ITS CODE OF ETHICS THAT APPLIES TO THE COMPANY'S PRINCIPAL EXECUTIVE OFFICER, PRINCIPAL FINANCIAL OFFICER, PRINCIPAL ACCOUNTING OFFICER OR ANY PERSON

PERFORMING SIMILAR FUNCTIONS, THE COMPANY INTENDS TO SATISFY ITS DISCLOSURE OBLIGATIONS, IF ANY, WITH RESPECT TO ANY SUCH WAIVER OR AMENDMENT BY POSTING SUCH INFORMATION ON ITS INTERNET WEBSITE SET

FORTH ABOVE RATHER THAN BY FILING A FORM 8-K.

